  "description": "Node-level system overview for the main homelab host: CPU/load, memory pressure, and filesystem capacity (root + backups) over time.\n\nData source: Prometheus via node_exporter. Disk capacity is based on available space (`node_filesystem_avail_bytes`) to reflect usable capacity for services.\n\nSecurity: Host and filesystem metrics can expose internal hostnames, mount points, and capacity posture. Restrict access and redact before sharing publicly.",
